| url=http://www.newsnet5.com/dpp/news/local_news/cleveland_metro/fbi-armenian-mob-style-crime-ring-steals-millions-in-northeast-ohio-73-indicted-nationwide
|title=FBI: Armenian 'mob style' crime ring steals millions in Northeast Ohio, 73 indicted nationwide 
|publisher=WEWS
|author=Dan Haggerty
|date=October 13, 2010 
